  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but some of the lines were something that [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] that the workers here, our heroes, in a way, and that we're not afraid so much of what they would do to us, because we know that the director will give us a ball to play, and so on.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After all, he's our friend-- which, of course, was satirical.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there were these kind of satirical songs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The tunes?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't remember what it came from.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I know, but like I say, if I would start singing, it would finish it right now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it goes something like-- [SINGING IN RUSSIAN] And so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was- but this, you could do only with young people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The older generation did not understand it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wanted to get another piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they would be dropping at the machines like flies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've seen it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
